{
  "stem": "26576.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Once the war finished, you could think that with all the problems that they gave to the Jews, that the place will be-- that the world will be a better place, but it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You were unwanted wherever you came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Paris was only a spot where you had to migrate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we intended-- we had two places in mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Either Canada or Australia, whichever, you know-- you needed a visa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we couldn't sit in Poland to wait for that visa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we picked Paris.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was just a matter-- and you couldn't go anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We didn't want Germany, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I've never set foot in Germany back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we picked Paris because that was the only reasonable place we got a visa for a certain period.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we stayed on in Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anyway, we came to Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was a very, again, a very terrible situation, because we came without money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We came without-- my mother was a very helpless woman always.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't know the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were completely on the mercy of the Joint, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we started to be migrant or refugee, whatever, all over again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if I think about Paris of that time, it real-- I think was very-- very unpleasant feelings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Although, at certain times, oh, it wasn't so bad, because we-- we had-- we-- I joined-- I was in the Bund, in the youth movement.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we went to visit places with this youth group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But in reality, one felt, all the time, that one is a refugee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "One felt unwanted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You had to go to the-- you had to-- every week, you had to tell the police-- tell them that you are alive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my husband was beaten.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The police were not nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
